OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,FSuspected cannabis with an estimated
OL,7,Fvalue of #4 million has been seized
OL,8,Ffollowing a cross-border police
OL,9,Foperation.
OL,11,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,12,F(PSNI) and An Garda Siochana
OL,13,Finvestigation uncovered the suspected
OL,14,Fdrugs on a lorry travelling from
OL,15,FScotland to Larne, Co Antrim, on
OL,16,FMonday.
OL,26,@tD@VrttD@Zrp
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
