OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,FA 53-year-old was arrested at the
OL,7,Fscene on suspicion of possession of a
OL,8,Fclass B controlled drug and possession
OL,9,Fof a controlled drug with intent to
OL,10,Fsupply.
OL,12,FHe remained in custody on Monday
OL,13,Fevening.
OL,15,FThe suspected drugs were found
OL,16,Fconcealed within a large number of
OL,17,Fboxes and are believed to have been
OL,18,Fdestined for the Republic of Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,F"We believe the drugs in this
OL,7,Fconsignment were intended to supply
OL,8,Fvarious organised crime groups across
OL,9,Fthe island of Ireland," the PSNI
OL,10,Fspokesperson said.
OL,12,F"The Joint Agency Task Force was
OL,13,Festablished with the aim of bringing a
OL,14,Fconcerted and enhanced effort to
OL,15,Ftackle cross-jurisdictional organised
OL,16,Fcrime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,F"All partners within the Task Force
OL,7,Fare totally committed to working
OL,8,Ftogether to reduce the misery caused
OL,9,Fby drug smuggling and to dismantle the
OL,10,Forganised groups profiting from this
OL,11,Ftype of criminality."
OL,13,FThey added: "We are delighted these
OL,14,Fdrugs have been removed from our
OL,15,Fstreets and that this income stream
OL,16,Fhas been denied to the criminal
OL,17,Fnetwork.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]uD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,F"It isn't difficult to imagine the
OL,7,Fharm that would have been caused by
OL,8,Fthis volume of drugs being dealt on
OL,9,Fstreet corners to vulnerable people,
OL,10,Fchildren and those with addiction
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"Some people may think that the
OL,14,Fillegal distribution of cannabis is
OL,15,Fnot a big deal. I'd ask them to just
OL,16,Ftake a moment to think about the
OL,17,Fviolence and exploitation that the
OL,18,Forganised criminals behind this could
OL,19,Fhave wreaked upon our communities with
OL,20,Fthe millions of pounds of profit they
OL,21,Fpotentially stood to make.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
