PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1777389066
OL,3,C#4m suspected drugs seized from lorry
OL,4,Cat Larne Port
OL,6,F"With the collective efforts of
OL,7,Fpartners, we'll work tirelessly to
OL,8,Ftackle such serious and organised
OL,9,Fcriminality and bring those
OL,10,Fresponsible to justice. We rely on the
OL,11,Fhelp of our community to do so and
OL,12,Fwould appeal to anyone with
OL,13,Finformation or concerns around illegal
OL,14,Fdrug supply to contact us on 101."
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
